          "name": "Charged Resolve",
          "description": "This unit gains 3 Charges. Triggered both at the very start of the battle if this unit is on the battlefield, and when this unit enters the battlefield from reinforcements. If this unit would be defeated while it has any charges, this unit will consume 1 charge to survive with 1HP remaining instead. Other skills may also be affected by and may consume charges. A unit can store up to 3 charges."
        }
      },
