        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Stealthy Vengeance",
          "description": "This unit gains the Stealth status effect and is Enraged, having its Attack increased to 1.5x until the end of its next turn. Allies gain 1 Spirit. All of these effects are triggered whenever another non-conjured Ally on the battlefield is defeated or sacrificed by any source. This may not trigger if this unit is defeated or sacrificed at the same time. This will overwrite other status effects and the effects of other Enrage skills on this unit. Stealthed units ignore the next enemy attack that would damage more than 1 target. Any damage will remove stealth."
